name: Dynamic Density [Spinning Section]
description:
A gigantic climbable structure crafted entirely in virtual reality and designed partly as a study of 3D printable Architecture. This design has been 3D printed multiple times successfully without any removable supports at sizes between 5 and 20cm tall. In virtual reality, the structure was experienced at about 300 meters tall.

The spinning section view allows us to see the inside, and all of the occupiable moments and smaller spaces.
